c-i-l acquiring trimac's stake in tricil
    toronto, march 25 - 
<c-i-l inc> said it would exercise its right to acquire <trimac ltd>'s
stake in their jointly owned tricil ltd for 91 mln dlrs, with closing
expected may 22. c-i-l added that the final price could be less,
however, depending on an ontario court ruling resulting from a
previously reported legal action launched by c-i-l. mississauga,
ontario-based tricil is a waste management company with operations in
the u.s. and canada. reuter 
